## Installation

<% if locales.keys == ['nii-core'] -%>
You do not need any additional libraries to use <%= l language %> with Nii.
All language data is included in `nii-core`.
<% elsif locales.size > 1 -%>
<% if included = locales['nii-core'] -%>
You do not need any additional libraries to use <%= l language %> with Nii.
<% end -%>
<% locales.except('nii-core').each do |source, list| -%>
However, you do need to install `<%= source %>` in order to use <%= l(list, list_style: :or) %>.
<% end -%>
See the [list of locales](#locales) below.
<% else -%>
In order to use <%= l language %> with Nii, you need to install `<%= locales.keys.first%>`.
<% end -%>
